                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4715" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1183</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9320 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“择”出新生：天津建材的混改战略抉择</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Choose” New Development: The Mixed Ownership Reform Strategic Choice of Tianjin Building Materials Group </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张璐，韩玉琪，乔晗(通讯作者)，胡景山，刘鑫，王伟楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津建材集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津建材；混合所有制改革；战略决策；战略投资者；2020百优案例；重点项目；系列4-1</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tianjin Building Materials; the Mixed Ownership Reform; Strategy Decision; Strategic Investor</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了天津市建筑材料集团（控股）有限公司（以下简称天津建材）在面临内部矛盾及外部困境时，为实现可持续发展，顺应国有企业改革大势，主动响应混改号召，决心实施混改的过程。为使集团获得更好的发展，天津建材领导班子主动迎接混改，统一集团舆论，获得大家对混改的认可，并就“改什么”、“怎么改”及“谁来改”等一系列重要问题开展相关工作，最终使混改顺利进行。本案例以天津建材的混改过程为主线，通过对天津建材混改的动因、混改方式的选择及战略投资者的遴选等内容进行分析，旨在引导学生利用战略分析工具、混改模式选择的影响因素及战略投资者等相关理论进行战略决策，以深入理解国企混改的战略逻辑。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case tells the story of Tianjin Building Materials Group (Holding) Co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as Tianjin Building Materials) in the face of internal contradictions and external difficulties, in order to achieve sustainable development, comply with the general trend of state-owned enterprise reform, take the initiative to respond to the call for mixed ownership reform, determined to implement the process of mixed ownership reform. In order to make the group get better development, the leading group of Tianjin Building Materials took the initiative to meet the mixed reform, unified the group public opinion, obtained everyone’s approval for the mixed reform, and carried out relevant work on a series of important issues such as “what to change”, “how to change” and “who will change”, so as to make the mixed ownership reform smoothly. Through the analysis of the motivation, the choice of mixed ownership reform mode and the selection of strategic investors, this case takes the mixing ownership reform process of Tianjin Building Materials as the main line, aims to guide students to make strategic decisions by using strategic analysis tools, influencing factors of mixed ownership reform mode selection and strategic investors, so as to deeply understand the strategic logic of mixed ownership reform of state-owned enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略决策、资源基础论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
